{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_10", "eventName": "破碎日冕", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "10-8", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "無暇哀悼", "storyInfo": "號角再次痛失戰友，決定救援被薩卡茲關押的其餘士兵。而羅德島與自救軍也準備展開行動，救援落入薩卡茲之手的信使海蒂·湯姆森。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g9_lightinduarea_street_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_053"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "頭兒，你說得沒錯，我們跟丟了。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那群反抗軍......一個個的，比沙地獸還狡猾。就這一會工夫，他們就跟鑽進沙堆裡似的，完全沒了影子。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......的確。所以，不要浪費精力。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在他們下一次冒頭之前，守好你們的位置。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_053"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，頭兒，你說了算。", "name": "薩卡茲雇傭兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_053"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來你找到了一批忠心耿耿的新屬下，“頭兒”。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們相信這裡會有好收成，這令他們滿懷鬥志。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們也很信任你。我看得很清楚，這份信任已經遠超一名雇傭兵對另一名雇傭兵該有的程度。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這說明曼弗雷德的計畫很奏效。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你對他的評價很高。差點忘了，你們已經是推心置腹的好朋友了，對吧？他分給你的新居所，光是書房就比你之前住的院子還大。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_393_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......那間伯爵宅邸，它的主人正是死在我手上。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#7$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別告訴我你的良心在發燙。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_393_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當時他正在喝下午茶......他的妻子和三個孩子就坐在他面前。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#2$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這的確不是我們過去接的那種活。但這是你自己選的，所以我們都沒資格為我們死去已久的良心哀悼。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就別問那樣的問題。你想確認什麼，直接看就好。你明明都知道。", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你壓力很大，我難道就好過？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，不跟你說這些。眼下可不是向彼此尋求安慰的時候。我來找你，是想提醒你一句——多看看腳下。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的意思是......", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雇傭兵總是沒那麼值得信任。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是走路的時候不多注意一下影子動向的話，小心功虧一簣。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_393_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你想告訴我的，就是這個？", "name": "赫德雷"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_393_1#3$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不止。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想說的是——兜兜轉轉這麼久以後，她在路上了。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g9_lightinduarea_street_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的人都就位了嗎？", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，都按薩卡茲的意思，去那個地點......", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別犯傻了，我說的不是薩卡茲要我們做的事。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長官，我們真的要在今晚行動嗎？會不會......", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你是想說，我們會不會中曼弗雷德的圈套？", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你以為我蠢到看不出他想做什麼嗎？", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有，我不敢......", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他是想試探我，我也會讓他試探。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的人會任他調遣......但他不知道我們到底有幾個人。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，我們還是得好好幫薩卡茲守門？", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......住嘴。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#7"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我非常討厭這個說法，聽起來就像我們是薩卡茲的......薩卡茲的......", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#7"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，算了。我們只需要忍這一天了。等辦完這最後一件事，我們就離開倫蒂尼姆。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#8"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真、真的嗎？長官，那我們可太高興了！", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我從小就很討厭倫蒂尼姆，我的爸爸媽媽都是來了這裡就沒回去過......", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個城市，它會吃人！", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嗯。我也不喜歡這裡。你見過哪一座城市像這樣，有這麼多地塊，這麼多高樓，這麼多排水溝的嗎？", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每次聞到那股......那股貴族餐桌上的油脂味，我都會犯噁心。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好在，我們終於可以走了。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傳話下去，晚上都給我“好好表現”。絕對不能讓曼弗雷德看出破綻。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另外挑十個最能打的，跟著我行動。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我讓你跟著曼弗雷德......你看清楚他剛才去哪裡了，沒錯吧？", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#2"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，長官。", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_406_1#1$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就好。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今天晚上......我一定要把我們的“間諜”救出來。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在倫蒂尼姆待了這麼久，總要做成一件事，才好心安理得地回家吧？", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_233_1#5"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我才不會讓領袖失望。", "name": "蔓德拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_233_1#5"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_warehouse", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "號角，你回來了！", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。羅本他們呢？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們也早就回來了。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。藥找到了嗎？我去看看薩利。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......你不用去了。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了？！你是說薩利他......", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還是得去看看他。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞又失去了一位好戰士。"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一位可愛的姑娘也失去了一位好父親。"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們到底還要失去多少，才能看到這場悲劇的尾聲？"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#5$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩利的女兒叫什麼名字？愛琳，還是艾爾莎？我記得他們一家住在阿斯卡拉郡。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#5$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "布萊克，麻煩你把薩利的遺物收起來，等戰爭結束，我們去一趟他家。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#5$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是......他什麼都沒留下來。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......什麼都沒有留下來？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#5$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，布萊克。他至少......留下了一段故事。我們還是得走一趟，他的女兒會想聽一聽......", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#5$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會告訴她，即使在最黑暗的時刻，她的父親都從未向苦痛低頭。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#5$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......好。我會陪你去，號角，我們等戰爭結束。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有，薩利他給你留了一句話。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他......他說了什麼？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他說——“中尉，對不起，但是請你活下去。”", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......他向我道歉。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#5$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。而且，我理解他。我們都理解他。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作為一名士兵，我們都想過，有一天可能會在哪裡戰死。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是經歷了這麼多以後，薩利他......不，我們都體會到了什麼才更可怕。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看看如今的倫蒂尼姆，它明明是我們的家，卻成了一座監獄。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對我們來說，光榮地戰死，是不是已經成了一種奢望？", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......本不該如此。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#5$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，但事實就是如此。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們明明都清楚這一點，卻還是......還是想要你堅持下去，因為是你給了我們希望。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "號角......你本來不用承擔我們這麼多人的希望。這太重了。", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "活下去......更難，是嗎？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈......看來我欠她一個道歉了。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她是誰？", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她和你們一樣，是最優秀的維多利亞士兵。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她......先不說這些。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴其他人，我們沒時間哀悼了。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "號角，你找到被關押的其他士兵的下落了？", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "機率很大。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我問出來的消息屬實，薩卡茲明天上午就會把人都轉移走。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我本來......我打算問一下你們的意見。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "號角，你不需要問，請直接下令吧！", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_422_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。等到天黑，我們立刻行動。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_4039_horn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "27_g6_hideout", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最有可能的關押位置我已在地圖上標明了，諸位還有沒有什麼看法？", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還剩下......八個地點嗎？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算加上我們的幹員，想在兩天之內排查完全部地點，也還是挺困難的。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很遺憾，這八個地點全都符合作為臨時監獄的條件。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們附近都沒有居民聚集區，這意味著很難有消息傳入傳出。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們同時也都位於通往中央區的幹道附近，這方便薩卡茲士兵在內外城區之間往來。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以及......它們都並不與我們所在的地塊連通。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩卡茲的指揮官猜到了你們會在地下活動？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_401_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他很聰明，我們絕不能小瞧他。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#8$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_401_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那......既然是用來關押俘虜的地方，是不是理應有重兵把守？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們也考慮過。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很遺憾，我們的偵察人員追蹤了薩卡茲士兵在各個區塊的行動路線，但都沒有發現破綻。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "這個位置是什麼地方？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line229"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一家廢棄工廠。以前據說是煉糖用的......對了，請不要誤會，這只是流傳在民用工業地帶的一種俗稱。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們煉製的是一種名為扭轉醇的有機化合物，只是因為包裝與深受孩子們喜愛的糖果近似，大家才戲稱他們在“煉糖”。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "煉糖廠？聽起來好耳熟......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "請把這裡列為首要排查的目標。;我們或許接近答案了。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line238", "option2": "line238"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_401_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "{@nickname}博士，能讓我知道為什麼嗎？", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#5$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我們可能認識這家煉糖廠的主人。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line244"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......我想起來了。您是說......托馬斯先生？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "托馬斯先生一直在為薩卡茲幹活，對不對？他說他看見薩卡茲在利用他的煉糖廠做一些事，而且他還因此差點被薩卡茲滅口。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再加上深池......深池也想要托馬斯先生身上的情報。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "所有站在薩卡茲對立面的勢力都想要......;......薩卡茲不希望別人得到的情報。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line252", "option2": "line252"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白了。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通知費斯特，我們的第一目標是製醇廠。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈默，你們的轉移工作繼續，我們依然隨時做好兩手準備......", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_398_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "指揮官！", "name": "自救軍戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_398_1#1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_401_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了，勞倫斯？", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#4$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_398_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "偵察小隊回來了，他們在地面上遇到了薩卡茲雇傭兵——", "name": "自救軍戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_398_1#1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_401_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......傷亡如何？", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#4$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_398_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "四人負傷，一人......被俘。", "name": "自救軍戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_398_1#1$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉了各位，會議中止，我得去看看......", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......指揮官。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_398_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "洛洛，你怎麼來了？你的傷口才剛包紮好！", "name": "自救軍戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_398_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不......我有消息要親口告訴指揮官。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_401_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們難道找到了......", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#3$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_401_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，我們得到了戈爾丁女士的消息。她還在北部居民區的學校裡，她很安全......", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他們在兩天前的一場聚會中，遭到了薩卡茲的突襲。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "信使女士她......被捕了。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_4040_rockr_1#10$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請等一下——", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們說的信使女士，就是委託你們接應羅德島的那位嗎？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#5$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "那位幫助羅德島進入維多利亞的女士。;那位搜集了許多維多利亞情報的女士。;那位凱爾希的老朋友。", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line302", "option2": "line302", "option3": "line302"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_401_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的......就是她。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#8$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿米婭，{@nickname}博士，我們的救援計畫得提前了。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#8$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她對自救軍非常重要。她掌握了許多情報，甚至可能影響到我們的撤離行動。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，我能理解......", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對羅德島來說，她也是不可或缺的。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_394_1#2$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "這將是我們第一次合作行動。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line314"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。我相信羅德島能幫助我們救回那位被薩卡茲關押的信使——", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們最堅強的戰士，最重要的同伴，最信任的朋友，海蒂·湯姆森女士。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}